casebody.data:
Juan Raicedo ACEBO-LEYVA
v.
Eric H. HOLDER, Jr., Attorney General. No. 13-877 R46-019. Supreme Court of the United States June 25, 2014.

Opinion

The petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Eleventh Circuit was dismissed today pursuant to Rule 46.1 of the Rules of this Court.
